    "Beware Of Gerovital H3r Imitations Professor Dr Ana Aslans medicinal preparation known as GEROVITAL H3 r is much aporeciated by the relevant cir cles in most of the countries of the world _ Following long studies and research in the treatment of old age and trophic phenomena and having at her disposal ev ery modern means of research Professor Dr Ana Aslan has obtained brilliant results work ing out anew method that has won recognition in world medi cal science GEROVITAL H3 r is insis tently sought after by numer ous clinics and doctors in var ious countries Asa result of the fame en joyed in this method of treat ment imitations and counter feits of the original product have cropped up in various countries and it became neces sary to take measures of legal protection and defence to pre vent the product and its author from being compromised GE ROVITAL H3 r thus came to be registered as a trade mark At present besides its inter national registration in Gene va valid in most of the coun tries that have adhered to the Madrid Arrangement namely Austria Belgium Czechoslova kia France the German Demo cratic Republic Hungary Italy Lichtenstein"
